Package index

AAGIS Regions

Fetch and read the ABARES Agricultural and Grazing Industries Survey (AAGIS) regions shapefile

read_aagis_regions()
Read 'Australian Agricultural and Grazing Industries Survey' (AAGIS) region mapping files

AGFD

Fetch

Fetch the Australian Gridded Farm Data (AGFD) NetCDF files

get_agfd()
Get 'Australian Gridded Farm Data' (AGFD) for local use

Read

Read the Australian Gridded Farm Data (AGFD) NetCDF files

read_agfd_dt()
Read 'Australian Gridded Farm Data' (AGFD) NCDF files as a data.table
read_agfd_stars()
Read 'Australian Gridded Farm Data' (AGFD) NCDF files with stars
read_agfd_terra()
Read 'Australian Gridded Farm Data' (AGFD) NCDF files with terra
read_agfd_tidync()
Read 'Australian Gridded Farm Data' (AGFD) NCDF files with tidync

Meta

Information about the AGFD NetCDF files and contents

print_agfd_nc_file_format()
Prints file format information for the AGFD NetCDF files

Topsoil Thickness

Get topsoil thickness for 'Australian Areas of Intensive Agriculture of Layer 1' for local use
read_topsoil_thickness_stars()
Read a 'Soil Thickness for Australian Areas of Intensive Agriculture of Layer 1' file with stars
read_topsoil_thickness_terra()
Read a Soil Thickness for Australian Areas of Intensive Agriculture of Layer 1 file with terra
print_topsoil_thickness_metadata()
Display complete metadata associated with soil thickness data
